name: Treasured Heart No. 3
description: I am 8 years old and one of my favorite things is to make other people laugh and smile.  Sometimes I tell jokes, or make silly faces, or show off my ballet moves.  Other times I make little presents and give them to my friends.  I never had any friends in Hic Et Nunc, so I want to give this heart to all my new friends in the NFT world!  with lots of love Jamboree!
